                        <h2>Azure Data Lake Storage<span>Azure Data Lake Storage</span></h2>
                        <h4>基于 Azure Blob 存储构建的高度可缩放的安全 Data Lake 功能</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_site_trial_storage-blobs">申请试用<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em>
